steps.description:
* Try to Kill on the way as many Zhevra and Raptors as Possible (careful high Mobs!)
* Avoid lvl 16+ Mobs as Possible
* Kill all Defender and Geomancer
* Kill Kreeing and Loot Item.
* Look for the CrossRoads Empty Supplies (Loot!)
* Go South To Ratchet (try to kill Zhevra and Raptors)
steps.tips:
* Try to Complete the Strider Quest, at this point
** South the Road are some...

steps.description:
* Turn In Quests 
* Accept New Quests!
* DON'T FORGET THE WANTED POSTER (left side, at the Bank)
* Move Southways

* Kill all Brigands and Cannoneers
* Kill Baron Longshore (Loot Head)
* Go back to Ratchet

* Go Straight to the north Building
* Turn in 2 Quests, Accept one New
* Go on the Peer, Turn in And Accept new Quest
* GO BACK TO the NORTH building Turn in And Accept new Quest
* Go back To the Pirates south

* Fight your way south to the Stolen Goods
* (Mouseover all Boxes at the Tents!)
* Go back To Ratchet

* Turn In Quest 
* use HS to CrossRoads

* Turn In Quests
* u must turn in the Strider quest, if not rdy (farm the missing , southwest are plenty)
* (if Raptor head quests rdy, turn in)
* Accept new Quests 
* BUY BAGS if you don't have 4 SIX slots bags
* Leave West way
* Repair and Resupply
steps.tips:
* YOU MUST be at least 14 at this point (if not, grind!) 
* TROLL/ORC if u need lvl 14 Skills, do the OG Ride quest
** (Mages, ride TO OG 14 SKILLS skills are important)

steps.description:
* Kill Strider / Raptor / Zhevra / Savannah (Cats) on your way for a Quest
* Don't need to complete Quest!
* Accept 2 Quests in Bunker
* Go North to the Oasis

* Kill Kolkar and Loot Item
* Loot Blue Mushrooms around the Water
* DIVE DOWN the lake to the Bubble Stone (Explore Oasis)
* Kill Barak, Loot HEAD (RED)
* Move West ways
steps.tips: * "Centaur Bracers" does not need to be completed now.

steps.description:
* Kill Harpy and Loot Claws
* After all Claws Obtained, move south, direction Stonetalon
* Grind your way South
steps.tips: * Only High lvl Raptors drop Horns (16+)

steps.description:
* Kill all Mobs you See
* Loot Raptor Horns and Zhevra hoof
* Some Strider are also nice to kill.
steps.tips: * Clear the Area; you don't need wait for respawn, just move on!

steps.description:
* Kill Ruffian And Mercenaries
* Go back and turn in quest accept new one
* Go again back INTO stonetalon!

* Fight your way through the Tauren 
* until you reach the Building with Kaya in It (YELLOW)
* kill the entire Camp and escort Kaya
* Go Back to the Barrens (Turn in Quests)
steps.tips:
* Kaya is a little Bitch with no HP, BE CAREFUL,
* in the Destroyed camp with kaya, 2 Tauren Spawn.
* Kaya cannot stand these attacks.. its HARD, if it failed.. skip quest!

steps.description:
* Grind Your way to the Bunker 
* Kill Strider / Raptors / Zhevras
* turn in Quests / Accept new One
* move to CrossRoads
steps.tips: * At this point the Zhevra Hoof MUST BE FINISH!

steps.description:
* Turn in Quest and Accept New one
* Move Southway out
steps.tips:
* Repair and sell Stuff
* Undead at flight Point has a TIMED quest to TB, accept it!

steps.description:
* Move South
* if you Raptor Horns Kill it on the way
* Find ManKirk's Wife (DEAD, BLUE)
* under ManKirk location there "StormSnout" kill it and Loot Quest Horn
* Move to Camp Tauroia (on the Street)
* Accept Flight Point
* Accept Quest (Dude in Cage)
* Move into Mulgore
* Move Strait to TB Elevator

* GO over the Bridge into the Cave in the North in TB
* ONLY turn in quest (don't accept any)
* Go to the Wind Rider Master 
* Use ur HeartStone! to CrossRoads
steps.tips: * Learn new Skills Here if u want. (Mage did not need it)

steps.description:
* Turn in Quest
* Leave XR west way

* Kill all Shavanna loot Quest Item (TUSK / CLAW)
* Grind through the Harpy to kill the SLAYER (loot Rings)
* Move out to a little Vendor (Sell Stuff)
steps.tips: * Only the Slayer drop the Ring

steps.description:
* Go to the Console, use it
* Turn in quest and accept new one
* use the 3 valves around the Machine,
* use the Console again; Turn in and Accept quest
* go to the Little house East, Kill Tinkerer (Loot Key)
* Go back to the Console, Use it Turn in and Accept quest

* Go East to the Shredder (Quest), Accept
* Move up the oil rig (in the Lake), Kill Supervisor (Loot Key)
* Jump Down to Shredder, Turn in Quest, Accept New (Follow quest)
* move west

* move West ways
* Kill Mobs until you can loot [Cats Eye Emerald]
* Move southway, to the Bridge

* Move south ways to the Bridge
* turn in quest  under the WatchTower
* Walk South to Ratchet
* turn in and Accept all Quests
* move West ways to the Oasis

* Go into the Oasis and Dive down (Bubble Stone ,BLUE)
* Kill Kolkar until Verog is Summoned! (he Spawn in the WEST)
* Finish the Kolkar Bracers Quest

* Turn in and Accept Quest
* Go Up the Watch Tower turn in and accept new quest
* repair and Sell Crap items
* Leave West way
steps.tips: * you can destroy [Dried Seeds] after the Oasis quest is turned in.

steps.description:
* Turn in Quests 
* Go north way to the Harpies!
* Kill Serena BloodFeather (Loot Head)
* Go Eastway

* Go eastway 
* if u Reach the Giant Dinosaur Skeletons, Use Horn in Inventory 
* Kill White Lion
* Use HeartStone to Crossroads
steps.tips: * Last Chance for the Raptor Heads! it its still open!

steps.description:
* Turn in Quest on Watch Tower + Accept new
* Turn in Quest  + Accept new
* Leave South way

* go on the Oasis and kill SnapJaw (Loot Item)
* Look for Hazrul and kill him.
* go South-East to the Raptor nests (kill a raptor for a feather, place into nest, repeat)
* Go South to the Raptor Hideout, Fight through and loot Stolen Silver
* Go East to the Northwatch
steps.tips: * Raptor Horns MUST be Complete by Now!

steps.description:
* Look for the Named Kodo (Lakota'mani) Kill and Loot Quest Item ( K )
* Kill the Bristleback and Loot the 60 Tusks
* Kill the Water Seeker / Geomancer (G) / Thornweaver (T)
* Go to Camp Tauroia
* Turn In quest / Accept ALL New
* u MUST at least 5 bars before 20, other wise grind the Bristlebacks (REALLY!) 
* Fly to CrossRoads
steps.tips:
* Keep the Blood shard (as many as you can) BUFF
* Spirit of the Wind is movement Speed
* Save some shards for later (10-20)

steps.description:
* Turn in Quests and Accept new Quests
* YOU MUST BE 20 BY NOW! otherwise Grind your way South to Tauroja!
* Fly to Thunderbluff

* Go South Turn in Quest; Accpet New
* Go To Your Class Trainer!
* Go to the Center Area (little pool) there is Quest NPC wandering around. (Turn In / Accept)
* Use HearthStone to CrossRoads
steps.tips:
* your Can Upgrade your first Aid if u want
    you need skill 80 for Wool Bandage

steps.description:
* Go Up all 3 Tower and Kill Named Mobs
* Kill Guards and loot Quest Item
* Go back West way and go South
* Go into the Stonetalon Mountains
steps.tips:
* Resupply / Repair in CrossRoads
* you should be around 15 quests by now (+-2), Excluded Dungeon quests
